Subject: [PATCH] ARM: atmel: add sama5d3 Xplained board support

Add sama5d3 Xplained board support which use Atmel SAMA5D36 SoC.
Now it supports boot from NAND flash and SD/MMC card.
Features support:
  - NAND flash
  - SD/MMC card
  - Two USB hosts
  - Ethernet (one GMAC, one EMAC)

